Stena, Koc Will Bid for Istanbul Ferry Company, Zaman Reports

-- B y   M a r k   B e n t l e y
-- 
2011-03-28T06:52:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/stena-koc-will-bid-for-istanbul-ferry-company-zaman-reports.html
Stena AB and  Turkey ’s  Koc Holding
AS (KCHOL)  will bid in an auction this month for Istanbul’s ferry
company IDO, Zaman newspaper reported.  Zorlu Holding, Yildirim Holding, UN Ro-Ro and Demiroren
Group, will also bid, the Istanbul-based newspaper said. Other
interested parties include TAV, Global Yatirim and RHEA Girisim
Sermayesi Yatirim Ortakligi, which plans to bid with  Greece ’s
Nel Lines, the Istanbul-based newspaper reported.    Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
